<h1 style=3D"color:#336699">Traveling Salesman Problem</h1>

<p>
The Traveling Salesman Problem, or TSP for short, is one of the most intens=
ively studied problems in computational mathematics.  These pages are devot=
ed to the history, applications, and current research of this challenge of =
finding the shortest route visiting each member of a collection of location=
s and returning to your starting point.
</p>=20


